1. Play with page builders: 
	- Elementor (Free)
	- Divi (Theme + Page Builder)


2. Try customizing a page with the page builder
	- Use the elementor to add styles 


3. Try customizing with REAL CSS 


4. Make a fully custom site with DIVI 


5. Practice a lot 

6. Start building Wordpress locally on your computer 
	Use Flywheel hosting and Local (a flywheel app) Easiest (recommended)
		- Edit the style sheet direction in a text editor 
		- Learn how to make a "child theme"
		- Save changes in GitHub  
		- Publish with Flywheel 

	
	
